¿Mana khuyapayakuqchu Dios kasharan Jobwan?
Manan. Jobpas chaytaqa yacharanmi.
Chaymi payqa imaymana llakipiña tarikuran chaypas niran: “Noqa kikiyta millakuni, ñut’u allpapi, usphapi tiyaykuspa, llakikuspa yuyayniyta jap’ikuni ”, nispa.
Chaypi rikusqanchis jina, Diosqa allintan Jobta yanaparan (Job 42: 1 - 6).
Elihupas ñan Jobtaqa yanapasqaña (Job 32: 5 - 10).
Chay yanapaykunata, consejokunatapas allinta chaskikusqanraykun Diosqa Jobta allinpaq qhawariran (Job 42: 7, 8).
¿Imaynatan Jobta yanapashallanman karan Diospa simin?
Diospa siminqa maytachá Jobtaqa kallpacharan.
“Ñaupaqmanta aswantaraq saminchapuran ” chaypas piensashallaranchá Diospa siminpiqa.
