Kanmi juj razonpas Jehová Dioslla gobernante kananpaqqa.
Payqa chanin Diosmi, pay kikinmi nin: “Noqa Señor Diosmi kani khuyapayakuqqa, kay pachapi chaninchaqpas kuskachaqpas, chaytapunin noqaqa munani ”, nispa (Jer.
